## Agent Routing (agentHint)

| Agent | Keywords | Use For |
|-------|----------|---------|
| **bolt** | infrastructure, deploy, kubernetes, database, cache, queue, storage | Task 1 (always), infra changes |
| **rex** | rust, axum, tokio, backend api | Rust microservices |
| **grizz** | go, grpc, chi | Go microservices |
| **nova** | node, bun, elysia, effect, typescript api | Node.js/Bun services |
| **blaze** | react, nextjs, frontend, ui, web | Web frontends |
| **tap** | expo, react native, mobile | Mobile apps |
| **spark** | electron, desktop | Desktop apps |
| **tess** | test, coverage, qa | Test implementation |
| **cipher** | security, auth, audit | Security review |
| **atlas** | merge, integrate, conflict | Final integration |

