- [ ] Every task has non-empty `testStrategy` with specific verification
- [ ] `agentHint` matches task content (not defaulting to rex)
- [ ] Dependencies form valid DAG (no cycles)
- [ ] Implementation tasks depend on task-001 (infrastructure)
- [ ] Frontend tasks depend on relevant backend API tasks
- [ ] Each task is atomic (completable in one PR)

